author: desruisseaux
msg: Simplification: try to be less surprising to the users:
- Getter methods clone the returned array, like what many libraries do.
- If no value (i.e. setValue(null) is invoked), unconditionally use the default value. Do not check anymore if the parameter is mandatory or optional.
